{"lemma":"تَأَنِّي","slug":"تَأَنِّي","root":"#.ن.#","root_slug":"_-ن-_","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ن-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n1406","n4135"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%A3%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%90%D9%91%D9%8A"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to act without haste, to be patient, to act leisurely, to be meticulous","examples":[{"text":"مَنْ تَأَنَّى نَالَ مَا تَمَنَّى.","english":"Slow and steady wins the race."},{"text":"فِي ٱلتَّأَنِّي ٱلسَّلَامَةُ وَفِي ٱلْعَجَلَةِ ٱلنَّدَامَةُ.","english":"In caution there is safety; in haste repentance."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ta.ʔan.naː/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n1406","headword_ar":"تانّى","root":"AnY","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He acted deliberately,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leisurely, not hastily;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstA^nY","text_ar":"استانى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aniYa","text_ar":"اَنِىَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaA^onaY","text_ar":"يَاْنَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^noYN","text_ar":"انْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he acted with moderation, gently, deliberately,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leisurely; without haste;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with gravity, staidness, sedateness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"calmness;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlA^amori","text_ar":"فِى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the affair;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstA^nY","text_ar":"استانى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he acted gently;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, T, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aniYa","text_ar":"اَنِىَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. and inf. n. as above: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he acted gently, and waited;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlA^amori","text_ar":"فِى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the affair:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he waited,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was patient,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waited with patience,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and did not hasten,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in an affair. (Msb.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~aA^at~iY","text_ar":"التَّاَتِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~aA^an~iY","text_ar":"التَّاَنِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"are nearly syn.: you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tA^n~Y lahu","text_ar":"تانّى لَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He acted gently with him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and did not hasten in his affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi","text_ar":"بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstA^nY","text_ar":"استانى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He waited patiently with him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waited, and had patience, with him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did not hasten him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstA^nAhu","text_ar":"استاناهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". ('Eyn, Har p. 67.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi HawolFA","text_ar":"بِهِ حَوْلًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ausotuw^oniYa","text_ar":"اُسْتُوْنِىَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was waited patiently with for a year"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY A^amorika","text_ar":"فِى اَمْرِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotaA^oni","text_ar":"اِسْتَاْنِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hasten not in thine affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlT~aEaAmi","text_ar":"فِى الطَّعَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotaA^onayotu","text_ar":"اِسْتَاْنَيْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I waited for the food to become perfectly prepared"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cooked."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 67.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taA^an~ayotu Alr~ajula","text_ar":"تَاَنَّيْتُ الرَّجُلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", M and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nZr","text_ar":"نظر"},{"kind":"text","text":", [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AinotaZarahu","text_ar":"اِنْتَظَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I waited for the man;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi","text_ar":"بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotaA^onayotu","text_ar":"اِسْتَاْنَيْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": whence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlojiraAHaAti","text_ar":"بِالْجِرَاحَاتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yusotaA^naY","text_ar":"يُسْتَانَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One should wait for the issues,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consequences,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"results, of wounds."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taA^n~ayotuka Hat~aY laA A^anaApa biY","text_ar":"تَانَّيْتُكَ حَتَّى لَا اَنَاةَ بِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have waited patiently for thee until there is no disposition to wait patiently in me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.)"}],"source_refs":["M","K","TA","Mgh","S","T","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n4135","headword_ar":"تَانِيٌ","root":"tnA^","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Remaining, staying, dwelling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abiding,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, Msb,) in a country, or town [&c.];"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"settling"},{"kind":"text","text":"therein: also pronounced"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taAnK","text_ar":"تَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", by suppression of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one who remains, stays,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abides, in his country,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"town;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Th, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dihoqaAnN","text_ar":"دِهْقَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a man having a fixed abode in a district of cultivated land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a village or town of such a district:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but see below]: (Th, K, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tun~aA='N","text_ar":"تُنَّا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, S, Msb, K.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layosa lilt~aAniy^api $aYo'N","text_ar":"لَيْسَ لِلتَّانِيَةِ شَىْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"For those who remain in their abodes, and go not forth with the soldiers on expeditions against the enemy, there shall be nothing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e., no share of the spoil. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rich; wealthy; possessing much property."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [Or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man possessing much land or other immoveable property:"},{"kind":"text","text":"for this is a signification assigned to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dihoqaAnN","text_ar":"دِهْقَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["T","Msb","Th","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}